## The Perfect Setting for Your Group

Camp Otyokwah hosts the Ignite Retreat for Jr. High students, plus custom group retreats year-round. Whether you are planning a youth weekend, a church getaway, or an organizational gathering, our beautiful wooded setting in Butler, Ohio provides an ideal environment for community, rest, and growth. Our retreats offer:

- Engaging teaching rooted in Scripture
- Awesome games and winter activities
- A more relaxed pace than summer camp
- Beautiful outdoor surroundings at Camp Otyokwah

