## Ignite Retreat

Ignite is our annual winter retreat for Jr. High students (grades 6–8). Get away from the busyness of life and experience Christ through worship, teaching, and community in a cozy winter setting.

- Dynamic worship and engaging teaching
- Blacklight dodgeball and indoor games
- Ice and snow activities
- Small group discussions
- Warm fellowship and great food

