## Facility Rentals & Custom Retreats

Looking to host your own retreat? Camp Otyokwah's facilities are available for custom group rentals year-round. From church youth groups to adult retreats to organizational gatherings, we can accommodate a wide range of groups and needs.

Contact us to discuss availability, pricing, and what we can offer your group.

- Lodging for groups of various sizes
- Full kitchen and dining hall
- Recreation areas and outdoor spaces
- Christ-centered environment

